        <h1>Ace Stream WebPlayer Guide</h1>
        <p>This is a webapp is a video player front-end for Ace Streams including a scraper which can provide a program
            list.</p>
        <h3>Limitations</h3>
        <p>If the stream has a codec that browsers don't support (AC3, DTS), audio will not work. Use an external media
            player.</p>
        <h3>Playing with an external media player</h3>
        <p>To play a stream with an external player, copy the Direct (stream) URL</p>
        <h4>VLC</h4>
        <p>On Computer, go to Media &gt; Open Network Stream, paste the Direct URL and click Open.</p>
        <p>On Mobile, go to Browse, Open Network Stream, Paste the Direct URL and click Open Network Stream</p>
        <h4>MPV</h4>
        <p>Run <code>mpv &lt;Direct URL&gt;</code> in a terminal.</p>
        <p>On MacOS you will first need to make a symlink to your path:<br>
            <code>sudo ln -s /Applications/mpv.app/Contents/MacOS/mpv /usr/local/bin/mpv</code>
        </p>
        <h3>IPTV</h3>
        <p>Not implemented yet</p>
